subject: Swimming
Weddings and Engagements
Olympic Games (2012)
lead_paragraph: The Olympic swimmer Matt Grevers decided he had to finish first in a meet last month, because he wanted to propose to his girlfriend and fellow swimmer Annie Chandler afterward.
